        Selling a Recently Renovated Property in Brisbane: What to Disclose and How to Market It
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A renovation can add significant value, but selling a recently renovated property comes with disclosure obligations and marketing considerations that sellers need to understand before they go to market.
      </p>
    </div>
